name: DisappointedParents
0:
”Alexa, launch my parents.”
”Alexa, open my parents.”
”Alexa, ask my parents if they are disappointed”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: my parents
des: If you're tired of getting too much validation from your parents, this is the skill for you! Whenever you're riding high or find yourself in an unusually good place either professionally or personally, just fire up this skill to put it all in perspective by letting you know that whatever your successes, they're still not good enough for your parents.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
